♪ Good morning, USA!

00:05.369 --> 00:09.272
♪ I got a feeling that it's
gonna be a wonderful day ♪

00:09.306 --> 00:12.241
♪ The sun in the sky
has a smile on his face ♪

00:12.276 --> 00:16.679
♪ And he's shining a salute
to the American race ♪

00:18.548 --> 00:21.951
♪ Oh, boy, it's swell to say

00:21.985 --> 00:23.953
♪ Good...
♪ Good morning, USA

